ScriptCommand.v_Query: select 'catos_customer' as tblName, concat(c.MA_KH, c.status)as id, c.if_seq as key, c.status as status, '0' as groups from fast_catos_customer c where c.if_fast_read = 'N' union all select 'catos_item' as tblName, concat(i.MA_VT, i.status)as id, i.if_seq as key, i.status as status, '0' as groups from fast_catos_item i where i.if_fast_read = 'N' union all select 'catos_vessel' as tblName, concat(v.MA_TAU, v.status)as id, v.if_seq as key, v.status as status, '0' as groups from fast_catos_vessel v where v.if_fast_read = 'N' union all select 'catos_invoice' as tblName, concat(r.key, r.status)as id, r.if_seq as key, r.status as status, '1' as groups from fast_catos_revenue r where r.if_fast_read = 'N'
